3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The fast marching algorithm has been used in computer vision for applications such as image segmentation and object tracking. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the implementation and complexity of the fast marching algorithm, which is a well-known algorithm in the field of data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) - The fast marching algorithm has been used in computer graphics for applications such as level set methods and shape modeling.
